<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٤٣٥⦘ قال" -<span class="c5">فذكر نحوه وقال:</span> - <span class="c1">"هل بلّغت"</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
